4 Forge Street is a leased industrial investment property with a new 5 year lease in a core Welshpool location.

The value of the investment is underpinned by its underlying land value and the lands proximity to Perth road, rail and airport infrastructure.

Prime industrial corner, just off both Orrong Road and Leach Highway in Welshpool. Improved with some 2,350sqm of industrial office/warehouse. This property provides the opportunity for investment and medium to long term capital growth and redevelopment/refurbishment potential.

KEY FEATURES
• New 5 year lease commencing expiring 14 March 2024 providing a net rental of $180,000 p.a.
• Corner site totaling 4,801sqm*
• Two street frontages totaling a combined 133.52 metres*
• A-grade industrial location just off Leach Highway, 15 minutes from Perth and in close proximity to Perth Airport and access to the Perth Road network
• Future refurbishment/subdivision/redevelopment potential
• Zoned "General Industrial"

The property is for sale by Private Treaty with an asking price of $2,450,000. For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*approx

CBRE has pleasure in offering for sale this strategically located vacant industrial lot situated in one of Perth's most well established and highly regarded industrial precincts.

18-20 Riversdale Road is nearby the Welshpool Road & Roe Highway Interchange and the soon to be upgraded Tonkin Highway and Roe Highway interchange.  The property has exposure to the Roe Highway.

Additional property features include:

- A vacant 5,671sqm* site
- Zoned General Industrial under the City of Canning's Town Planning Scheme
- Benefits from a 207 metre* combined street frontage to both Riversdale and Glenferrie Roads.
- Exposure to Roe Highway
